dct_title_s: Colton's township map of Oregon & Washington Territory
dct_description_sm: prepared by G.W. & C.B. Colton & Co., New York.
Brown line print made in 1976 by Desert Enterprises, Ontario, Calif.
Hachured. Shows ocean, river & rail lines operating & projected.
